  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Colon cancer is a very common cancer. Prognosis and adjuvant treatment depend on the
      pathological results. Histoprognostic new factors have recently been published by several
      authors, but their validity is still debated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
